            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>This is also not a call to action to burn all of your Vineyard Vines clothing. Wear whatever you want. I’m just one overly opinionated college sophomore with a column making a statement. A statement that is far less obnoxious and sh*tty than owning 3 mint-colored, whale-themed long-sleeve tees.</p>
<p><em>Sami Kirkpatrick is a Trinity sophomore. His column runs on alternate Wednesdays.</em></p>

